3) Functionalități pe pagini (cerințe & acceptance)

3.1 Home (MVP)

Secțiuni recomandate:
	1.	Hero full-bleed (video opțional) + headline + CTA primar (“Enquire”) + CTA secundar (“View yachts”)
	2.	“Featured Yachts” (4–6 cards)
	3.	“Destinations” (5 cards/carousel)
	4.	“Why Mediterana” (3–5 bullets + trust signals)
	5.	“The Process” (3 pași: Discover → Match → Charter) inspirat din abordările tip “guide/process”.  ￼
	6.	Latest blog posts (3)
	7.	Footer lux (newsletter optional)

Acceptance:
	•	CTA sticky în header (desktop) + buton simplu pe mobil
	•	Hero optimizat (LCP < 2.5s pe 4G)
	•	Toate secțiunile editabile din CMS

3.2 About
	•	Poveste (brand positioning)
	•	“What we do” (Charter / Corporate / Day trips / Events – dacă vrei)
	•	“How we work” (proces)
	•	Trust: experiență, parteneri, disclaimers

Acceptance: conținut 100% CMS, imagini optimizate.

3.3 Yachts (grid /yachts)

MVP:
	•	Grid cards cu: imagine principală, nume, tip (motor/sailing/catamaran), lungime, guests, cabin, “From €” (dacă există), CTA “View”.
	•	Filtre simple (client-side): Type, Guests, Length range (optional).
	•	Sort: Featured, Length, Guests.

Acceptance:
	•	20 yacht-uri randate rapid (SSG/ISR)
	•	Filtre fără refresh pagină
	•	URL query params pt filtre (shareable): ?type=catamaran&guests=8

3.4 Yacht detail /yachts/[slug]

Layout recomandat (lux editorial):
	•	Hero gallery (carousel) + quick facts
	•	Descriere editorială
	•	Specs table (structured)
	•	“Highlights” (3–6)
	•	“Onboard Experience” (text + 2 imagini)
	•	Video placeholder (YouTube/Vimeo embed)
	•	CTA final: “Request availability / Get a quote” (form scurt)

Acceptance:
	•	Galerie performantă (lazy + blur placeholders)
	•	Form precompletat cu yachtName
	•	SEO: title/description, OG image, JSON-LD (Product/Service)

3.5 Destinații (/destinations + /destinations/[slug])
	•	Pagina listă: 5 zone cu imagery mare + best season + 3 highlights
	•	Pagină destinație:
	•	Hero
	•	“Why go” + “Best time to visit”
	•	Suggested itinerary (3–7 zile)
	•	Featured yachts for this destination (manual curated)
	•	CTA: “Plan your charter”

Acceptance: posibilitate de a lega yachts ↔ destinations în CMS.

3.6 Blog
	•	/blog: list + categories/tags + search (optional)
	•	/blog/[slug]: articol + table of contents (auto) + CTA

Acceptance: draft/preview, SEO bun, imagini optimizate.

3.7 Contact
	•	Form: nume, email, telefon (optional), mesaj, interes (Yacht/Destination/General), date (optional)
	•	Map embed (optional)
	•	Contact details + WhatsApp link

Acceptance: anti-spam (hCaptcha/Turnstile), email delivery + notificare.

