4) Content model (CMS)

Recomand Sanity CMS (rapid, schemă în cod, preview bun) + Next.js ISR.

Tipuri (documente)
	•	siteSettings: logo, social, SEO default, featured yacht IDs
	•	page: Home/About/Contact (sections)
	•	yacht:
	•	name, slug, featured (bool)
	•	heroMedia: [images], videoUrl
	•	summary, description (rich text)
	•	specs: length, beam, draft, year, guests, cabins, crew, cruisingSpeed
	•	pricing: fromPrice (optional), currency, priceNote
	•	destinations: [ref destination]
	•	destination:
	•	name, slug, heroImage
	•	bestSeason, highlights, itinerary (rich)
	•	gallery
	•	post:
	•	title, slug, excerpt, body, coverImage, tags, publishedAt, author

