6) Tech stack (recomandat pentru execuție rapidă)

Frontend
	•	Next.js (App Router) + TypeScript
	•	Styling: TailwindCSS + shadcn/ui (componente curate, ușor de adaptat “lux”)
	•	Animations: Framer Motion (doar unde ajută)
	•	Images: next/image + responsive sizing
	•	SEO: next/metadata, OG images generate (opțional)

CMS & conținut
	•	Sanity (hosted) + @sanity/next preview
	•	Media: Sanity assets (CDN) + reguli de crop

Forms / lead handling
	•	API route /api/inquiry
	•	Email provider: Resend (sau SendGrid)
	•	Stocare lead-uri:
	•	MVP: trimis pe email + opțional Google Sheets via webhook
	•	v1: HubSpot / Pipedrive integration

Analytics & tracking
	•	Plausible (simplu, privacy) sau GA4
	•	Event tracking: cta_click, inquiry_submit, yacht_view

Quality
	•	ESLint + Prettier
	•	Playwright (smoke tests: nav + form)
	•	Lighthouse CI (optional)

⸻

7) Arhitectură (simplă, scalabilă)

Next.js:
	•	Pages statice + ISR pentru /yachts, /destinations, /blog
	•	Dynamic routes: [slug] cu generateStaticParams + revalidate
	•	Caching: Next + Vercel Edge cache
	•	Search/filters: client-side pe dataset mic (~20); server-side dacă crește.

Data flow:
Sanity → Next.js (GROQ queries) → render (SSG/ISR) → user → inquiry API → email/CRM.

