	•	Setup Next.js + Tailwind + shadcn
	•	Sanity schemas + seed content (20 yachts, 5 destinations, 6–10 blog posts)
	•	Implement pagini 6 + dynamic slugs
	•	Inquiry form + email delivery + anti-spam
	•	Basic SEO + OG
	•	Performance pass (images/video)

v1 (upgrade)
	•	Multi-language (RO/EN) dacă vrei piață internațională
